org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.HRM.HwLogical.HwStorage.HwMemory

Interface HwRAM

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, HwMemory, HwResource, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource, StorageResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HwRAMImpl

    public interface HwRAM
extends HwMemory
    A representation of the model object 'Hw RAM'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Organization
    • Is Synchronous
    • Is Static
    • Is Non Volatile
    • Repl Policy
    • Write Policy

    See Also:
    HwMemoryPackage.getHwRAM()
